message.body: Good job in the video!!
Thanks. I'm getting mixed feedback
It was a lot shorter than the others
Yeah its just his intro to his CD he's about to finish
O ok.. Makes sense.. What's everyone saying about it?
Some ppl said there should be more scenes...some ppl said theme doesn't match song. Will thinks intro to rap pin too long. Kurt didn't like his performance...
Some ppl said its coolest one yet so ppl are say in diff stuff
It's not my fav but I still think u did a good job.. Do u is still mos def hands down my fav
What did u like about do u?
I thought the quality was great, all the scenes and the flashbacks

Yeah alotta ppl seemed to like that one. I like it too. I like the new one a lot. I think it has some really cool imagery and I matched the vid up with the beat pretty well. Kurt has good energy. Tryna do something a lil doff each time
That's a good idea .. U want to be able to catch the attention from different crowds and taste so that's the best way to do it
Word I hope u dun mind me tagging you
Lol not at all ;-)
My friends watched the first time u tagged me in the do u video n they loved it... Especially the ones from Philly
Sweet. So what is goin on with you?
Nothin really.. I got promoted at work, which is cool I guess.. Tay starts tball so I'm going to be busy with that and her dance class soon
How about u?
Oh yeah life is good? I haven't seen u in awhile
I knnoowwww!! I was thinking that the other day.. Why r u doin for ur bday?
I might goto this concert on Saturday. But nothing crazy. U tryna hang out. Keep the annual tradition alive?? Haha

I wish I could but this wknd is extra busy for me.. Tay has opening day for tball Saturday morning, my nieces sweet 16 is Saturday night and then I'm throwing a baby shower for my cousin Sunday afternoon :-/
Well my bday is Monday...
Lol I know.. When r u celebrating it??
Saturday but we can always mini celebrate a diff day lol
Lol
Ok
